{"componentChunkName":"component---src-templates-page-js","path":"/2015/10/06/Hexo-Install_Hexo/","result":{"data":{"markdownRemark":{"frontmatter":{"title":"Hexo - 安裝 Hexo","date":"06 October 2015","author":"Sky Chang","excerpt":null,"tags":["Node.js","Hexo","Github"],"coverImage":null},"id":"9caa1c58-ec83-5a72-a48f-f1b01f3359f6","html":"<h2>前言</h2>\n<p>用了很長一段的 Blogger ，目前也已經停止使用了，至於為什麼，有興趣的朋友可以去<a href=\"http://blog.sanc.idv.tw\">舊站</a>看看，大體來說，就是小弟希望能用 Markdown 當作 Source Code 的方式把文章留下來，以前在 Blogger 撰寫，雖然寫得很愉快，但貼上後，就是 HTML 格式了，對於未來想轉移，其實都很不方便。而後來看了很多的架站方案，基本上小弟我也不喜歡太複雜的...前後有嘗試過 Hugo ，但是 Hugo 搬移文章的工具，小弟我根本不知道該怎麼使用!!(遮臉) ，所以後來還是選擇了以 Node.js 為核心的 Hexo ，選擇 Hexo 的原因其實很簡單，主要是因為目前已經維護得很穩定，而且也有眾多文件。最後選擇架設在 GitHub 上面，其實也沒有甚麼特別的原因，只是因為他很佈署，又方便 XDDD.</p>\n<p>這篇主要是紀錄一下自己的使用過程，雖然市面上已經有很多人寫過類似的文章了，但是有的時候，一些小設定，每次都要 Google 還是很麻煩的，所以就邊架設的過程中，就順便紀錄一下。</p>\n<h2>Hexo</h2>\n<p>Hexo 是基於 Node.js 開發的套件，它可以將 Markdown 轉成 HTML，而且提供了豐富的工具。\n有興趣的朋友，也可以直接參考<a href=\"https://hexo.io/\">官網</a></p>\n<h2>安裝</h2>\n<p>首先，我們使用以下指令來安裝，當然，既然底層是 Node.js ，當然就是用 <code class=\"language-text\">npm</code> 了。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"yml\"><pre class=\"language-yml\"><code class=\"language-yml\"><span class=\"token key atrule\">language</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> node_js\n\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">node_js</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span> stable\n\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">script</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span> npm install\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span> hexo cl\n\n<span class=\"token key atrule\">after_success</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">:</span>\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span> git config <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>global user.name \"yourName\" \n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span> git config <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>global user.email \"your Mail\"\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span> sed <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>i'' \"/^ <span class=\"token important\">*repo/s~github\\.com~$</span><span class=\"token punctuation\">{</span>GH_TOKEN<span class=\"token punctuation\">}</span>@github.com~\" _config.yml\n  <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span> hexo deploy <span class=\"token punctuation\">-</span>g</code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/4a6e32130183bd6baa1a669acaa76fb1/1d5a8/01.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 61.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"01\"\n        title=\"01\"\n        src=\"/static/4a6e32130183bd6baa1a669acaa76fb1/78d47/01.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4a6e32130183bd6baa1a669acaa76fb1/56d15/01.png 200w,\n/static/4a6e32130183bd6baa1a669acaa76fb1/d9f49/01.png 400w,\n/static/4a6e32130183bd6baa1a669acaa76fb1/78d47/01.png 800w,\n/static/4a6e32130183bd6baa1a669acaa76fb1/1d5a8/01.png 979w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>完成之後，就可以使用 <code class=\"language-text\">hexo init</code> 名稱 來建置</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">hexo init blog</code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/80ae21848c3adc2bcc9b02c2bf2adbf6/1d5a8/02.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 61.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"02\"\n        title=\"02\"\n        src=\"/static/80ae21848c3adc2bcc9b02c2bf2adbf6/78d47/02.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/80ae21848c3adc2bcc9b02c2bf2adbf6/56d15/02.png 200w,\n/static/80ae21848c3adc2bcc9b02c2bf2adbf6/d9f49/02.png 400w,\n/static/80ae21848c3adc2bcc9b02c2bf2adbf6/78d47/02.png 800w,\n/static/80ae21848c3adc2bcc9b02c2bf2adbf6/1d5a8/02.png 979w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>接下來，我們要進入剛剛建立好的 blog 目錄底下，並輸入 <code class=\"language-text\">npm install</code> 來進行載入套件。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">npm install</code></pre></div>\n<p>這邊要特別注意一下，如果是使用 OSX 環境的朋友，請安裝 XCode 和 XCode Command Line 工具，不然會發生錯誤。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a5a6500765e4972a0755403b2846d3ea/1d5a8/03.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 61.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"03\"\n        title=\"03\"\n        src=\"/static/a5a6500765e4972a0755403b2846d3ea/78d47/03.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a5a6500765e4972a0755403b2846d3ea/56d15/03.png 200w,\n/static/a5a6500765e4972a0755403b2846d3ea/d9f49/03.png 400w,\n/static/a5a6500765e4972a0755403b2846d3ea/78d47/03.png 800w,\n/static/a5a6500765e4972a0755403b2846d3ea/1d5a8/03.png 979w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>接著，我們可以簡單的使用 hexo server 來啟動 LocalHost 的 Server ，預設會在 localhost:4000 的位置，另外，雖然如下圖，訊息會 show 出 run 在 0.0.0.0:4000 ，但如果是 windows 環境，還是必須要打 localhost:4000。</p>\n<p>( 0.0.0.0 代表的是可以從任何地方進行瀏覽此網站，localhost 代表的是只能從本地瀏覽此網站，無法從外部瀏覽 )</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">hexo Server</code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/57cf49283db8b74ba05e79bbcc106c0e/1d5a8/04.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 61.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"04\"\n        title=\"04\"\n        src=\"/static/57cf49283db8b74ba05e79bbcc106c0e/78d47/04.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/57cf49283db8b74ba05e79bbcc106c0e/56d15/04.png 200w,\n/static/57cf49283db8b74ba05e79bbcc106c0e/d9f49/04.png 400w,\n/static/57cf49283db8b74ba05e79bbcc106c0e/78d47/04.png 800w,\n/static/57cf49283db8b74ba05e79bbcc106c0e/1d5a8/04.png 979w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>更換主題</h2>\n<p>如果用瀏覽器看，沒啥問題，我們就可以開始挑選喜歡的佈景主題，小弟這邊的主題是 <a href=\"https://github.com/iissnan/hexo-theme-next\">Next 主題</a>。</p>\n<p>這邊你可以選擇 clone 或是，基本的 Download ，小弟是直接透過 Download 的方式。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/154e59e053a910759bc28a4877c47eb3/3b5a6/05.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 54%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"05\"\n        title=\"05\"\n        src=\"/static/154e59e053a910759bc28a4877c47eb3/78d47/05.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/154e59e053a910759bc28a4877c47eb3/56d15/05.png 200w,\n/static/154e59e053a910759bc28a4877c47eb3/d9f49/05.png 400w,\n/static/154e59e053a910759bc28a4877c47eb3/78d47/05.png 800w,\n/static/154e59e053a910759bc28a4877c47eb3/64756/05.png 1200w,\n/static/154e59e053a910759bc28a4877c47eb3/3b5a6/05.png 1302w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>下載下來的檔案，解壓縮後，要把它放到 Theme 的目錄底下，並且改名成 Next。</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/a53c0d622d784c6d8cce9ecb32b3708d/9dba0/06.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 45.49999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"06\"\n        title=\"06\"\n        src=\"/static/a53c0d622d784c6d8cce9ecb32b3708d/78d47/06.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/a53c0d622d784c6d8cce9ecb32b3708d/56d15/06.png 200w,\n/static/a53c0d622d784c6d8cce9ecb32b3708d/d9f49/06.png 400w,\n/static/a53c0d622d784c6d8cce9ecb32b3708d/78d47/06.png 800w,\n/static/a53c0d622d784c6d8cce9ecb32b3708d/64756/06.png 1200w,\n/static/a53c0d622d784c6d8cce9ecb32b3708d/9dba0/06.png 1299w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>接下來，修改 _config.yml 檔案，找到 Theme ，並把它改成 Next。\n( 當然，不一定要用記事本，小弟這邊是懶得用其他工具，就直接開了~ )</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/4834ba22b0cdbdf83b97661b52ebc5b7/1d5a8/07.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 61.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"07\"\n        title=\"07\"\n        src=\"/static/4834ba22b0cdbdf83b97661b52ebc5b7/78d47/07.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4834ba22b0cdbdf83b97661b52ebc5b7/56d15/07.png 200w,\n/static/4834ba22b0cdbdf83b97661b52ebc5b7/d9f49/07.png 400w,\n/static/4834ba22b0cdbdf83b97661b52ebc5b7/78d47/07.png 800w,\n/static/4834ba22b0cdbdf83b97661b52ebc5b7/1d5a8/07.png 979w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>接著，我們就可以使用 hexo s --debug 來開啟 Server，加上 debug 會產生輸出 log 的效果，而 s 是 server 的簡寫。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">hexo s --debug</code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/5db3ae2564f0a59f73c2c9a1ff58025c/1d5a8/08.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 61.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"08\"\n        title=\"08\"\n        src=\"/static/5db3ae2564f0a59f73c2c9a1ff58025c/78d47/08.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/5db3ae2564f0a59f73c2c9a1ff58025c/56d15/08.png 200w,\n/static/5db3ae2564f0a59f73c2c9a1ff58025c/d9f49/08.png 400w,\n/static/5db3ae2564f0a59f73c2c9a1ff58025c/78d47/08.png 800w,\n/static/5db3ae2564f0a59f73c2c9a1ff58025c/1d5a8/08.png 979w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>然後就可以看到漂漂的網站嚕!! ( 至少小弟是滿喜歡這種簡潔風格的.... )</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/4695a2caf726a645187bfb2cfc605a77/95b97/09.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 58.50000000000001%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"09\"\n        title=\"09\"\n        src=\"/static/4695a2caf726a645187bfb2cfc605a77/78d47/09.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4695a2caf726a645187bfb2cfc605a77/56d15/09.png 200w,\n/static/4695a2caf726a645187bfb2cfc605a77/d9f49/09.png 400w,\n/static/4695a2caf726a645187bfb2cfc605a77/78d47/09.png 800w,\n/static/4695a2caf726a645187bfb2cfc605a77/64756/09.png 1200w,\n/static/4695a2caf726a645187bfb2cfc605a77/95b97/09.png 1283w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<h2>匯入資料</h2>\n<p>接下來，我們可以把原本的 Blogger 或是 WordPress 的資料移入進來。</p>\n<p>如果要載入 Blogger ，小弟建議使用 RSS 讀讀入套件 ( Hexo 也只有這個方法.... )\n所以我們要先裝一下 <code class=\"language-text\">hexo-migrator-rss</code> 這個 package。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">npm install hexo-migrator-rss --save</code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/1ac857e43da79ccd9af437b97ee4a175/1d5a8/10.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 61.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"10\"\n        title=\"10\"\n        src=\"/static/1ac857e43da79ccd9af437b97ee4a175/78d47/10.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/1ac857e43da79ccd9af437b97ee4a175/56d15/10.png 200w,\n/static/1ac857e43da79ccd9af437b97ee4a175/d9f49/10.png 400w,\n/static/1ac857e43da79ccd9af437b97ee4a175/78d47/10.png 800w,\n/static/1ac857e43da79ccd9af437b97ee4a175/1d5a8/10.png 979w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>裝完之後，我們就可以使用下圖的命令讀入 Blogger 的文章。\n( 通常如果沒給 max-result ，只會讀入少量的文章，所以這邊透過設定 max-result 的方式，來讀入所有文章 )</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/84717a16fb750953a31a89336e214332/0b602/11.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 54.49999999999999%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,iVBORw0KGgoAAAANSUhEUgAAABQAAAALCAYAAAB/Ca1DAAAACXBIWXMAAA7EAAAOxAGVKw4bAAAAfklEQVQoz+2OTQrCUAyEk/fiZUQ3SqveUfCnVsEmeepCvOVos/AA2p0ODF8g8DG03mzRHk9oDm2wU4O6ozPDWTWo5m+al/jHXUrQL1fs9g1u9wfoFQzV8WQKyjICM4NTQvqwIhLCarkCpSxfL+ulPWdVDeKcBxPO68Vf+BPCJ2ERBo6M1nyeAAAAAElFTkSuQmCC'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"11\"\n        title=\"11\"\n        src=\"/static/84717a16fb750953a31a89336e214332/78d47/11.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/84717a16fb750953a31a89336e214332/56d15/11.png 200w,\n/static/84717a16fb750953a31a89336e214332/d9f49/11.png 400w,\n/static/84717a16fb750953a31a89336e214332/78d47/11.png 800w,\n/static/84717a16fb750953a31a89336e214332/0b602/11.png 1105w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>如果是要轉入 WordPress 則要安裝 <code class=\"language-text\">hexo-migrator-wordpress</code> 套件。</p>\n<div class=\"gatsby-highlight\" data-language=\"text\"><pre class=\"language-text\"><code class=\"language-text\">npm install hexo-migrator-wordpress --save</code></pre></div>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/00f389cb0274598a2b2beb20464577bd/1d5a8/12.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 61.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"12\"\n        title=\"12\"\n        src=\"/static/00f389cb0274598a2b2beb20464577bd/78d47/12.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/00f389cb0274598a2b2beb20464577bd/56d15/12.png 200w,\n/static/00f389cb0274598a2b2beb20464577bd/d9f49/12.png 400w,\n/static/00f389cb0274598a2b2beb20464577bd/78d47/12.png 800w,\n/static/00f389cb0274598a2b2beb20464577bd/1d5a8/12.png 979w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>接下來，我們只要輸入如下圖的指令。\n( 別忘了要先去 WordPress 把文章備份出來 )</p>\n<p><span\n      class=\"gatsby-resp-image-wrapper\"\n      style=\"position: relative; display: block; margin-left: auto; margin-right: auto; max-width: 800px; \"\n    >\n      <a\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-link\"\n    href=\"/static/4f20a2c80b8cd8294d2c20585e6f998d/1d5a8/13.png\"\n    style=\"display: block\"\n    target=\"_blank\"\n    rel=\"noopener\"\n  >\n    <span\n    class=\"gatsby-resp-image-background-image\"\n    style=\"padding-bottom: 61.5%; position: relative; bottom: 0; left: 0; background-image: url('data:image/png;base64,'); background-size: cover; display: block;\"\n  ></span>\n  <img\n        class=\"gatsby-resp-image-image\"\n        alt=\"13\"\n        title=\"13\"\n        src=\"/static/4f20a2c80b8cd8294d2c20585e6f998d/78d47/13.png\"\n        srcset=\"/static/4f20a2c80b8cd8294d2c20585e6f998d/56d15/13.png 200w,\n/static/4f20a2c80b8cd8294d2c20585e6f998d/d9f49/13.png 400w,\n/static/4f20a2c80b8cd8294d2c20585e6f998d/78d47/13.png 800w,\n/static/4f20a2c80b8cd8294d2c20585e6f998d/1d5a8/13.png 979w\"\n        sizes=\"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px\"\n        style=\"width:100%;height:100%;margin:0;vertical-align:middle;position:absolute;top:0;left:0;\"\n        loading=\"lazy\"\n      />\n  </a>\n    </span></p>\n<p>基本上，這樣子文章的轉移，就差不多完成了，但要注意一下，透過 rss 的方式，並不會把圖檔也載下來，簡單的說，就是圖檔還是在原本的圖庫裡面，還是透過超連結取得圖檔。但如果是從 Wordpress的方式載入進來的話，基本上是可以連圖檔一起進來的...</p>\n<p>基本上，這篇先到這邊! 我們完成了文章的載入，那又要怎樣佈署上去呢?!</p>\n<p>下一篇，我們將介紹如何上傳到 GitHub 上，並且正式發佈。</p>\n<h2>參考資料</h2>\n<ul>\n<li><a href=\"http://serverfault.com/questions/78048/whats-the-difference-between-ip-address-0-0-0-0-and-127-0-0-1#comment63540_78049\">http://serverfault.com/questions/78048/whats-the-difference-between-ip-address-0-0-0-0-and-127-0-0-1#comment63540_78049</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"http://wsgzao.github.io/post/hexo-guide/\">http://wsgzao.github.io/post/hexo-guide/</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://github.com/iissnan/hexo-theme-next\">https://github.com/iissnan/hexo-theme-next</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://git-scm.com/book/zh-tw/v1/%E4%BC%BA%E6%9C%8D%E5%99%A8%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84-Git-%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90-SSH-%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E9%87%91%E9%91%B0\">https://git-scm.com/book/zh-tw/v1/%E4%BC%BA%E6%9C%8D%E5%99%A8%E4%B8%8A%E7%9A%84-Git-%E7%94%9F%E6%88%90-SSH-%E5%85%AC%E9%96%8B%E9%87%91%E9%91%B0</a></li>\n<li><a href=\"https://gist.github.com/adamjohnson/5682757\">https://gist.github.com/adamjohnson/5682757</a></li>\n</ul>","excerpt":"前言 用了很長一段的 Blogger ，目前也已經停止使用了，至於為什麼，有興趣的朋友可以去舊站看看，大體來說，就是小弟希望能用 Markdown 當作 Source Code 的方式把文章留下來，以前在 Blogger 撰寫，雖然寫得很愉快，但貼上後，就是 HTML…"}},"pageContext":{"type":"posts","next":{"frontmatter":{"path":null,"title":"Webpack - 使用 Webpack Dev Server 進行開發","tags":["JavaScript","Webpack","CSS","HTML"]},"fields":{"slug":"/2015/08/27/Webpack-dev_server/"},"fileAbsolutePath":"/home/runner/work/blog.sanc.idv.tw/blog.sanc.idv.tw/src/posts/Webpack-dev_server/Webpack-dev_server.md"},"previous":{"frontmatter":{"path":null,"title":"Hexo - 版本控制與發佈到 GitHub","tags":["Node.js","Hexo","GitHub"]},"fields":{"slug":"/2015/10/19/Hexo-Source_Control_and_Deploy/"},"fileAbsolutePath":"/home/runner/work/blog.sanc.idv.tw/blog.sanc.idv.tw/src/posts/Hexo-Source_Control_and_Deploy/Hexo-Source_Control_and_Deploy.md"}}}}